etimes and industrial dynamics. The theory is placed\nin the context of the multi-level perspective on technology transitions, where\ninnovation and the diffusion of new socio-technical regimes take a prominent\nplace, as well as discrete choice theory, the primary theoretical framework for\nintroducing agent diversity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2013 10:44:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2013 17:30:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 1 Nov 2013 17:29:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Nov 2014 12:54:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-23"}
